2623930_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=HUDq780gky0Q7kNvgF4EkGo&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC3sIyFWYQjg7R2Pos2dLuyX5ImFQhkMLsjaU1xt-3ryQ&oe=67714E7E"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "CoverArt_Landscape_0.png", "id": "1502591547345462", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75416835_1502591550678795_714131516175272875_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=D81yy1M4TTkQ7kNvgElsF8T&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD-9mYYlH8HbhqDxWleb3tP96oXh7s_wk4KQ9UKy9vD_g&oe=67713B83"}, "display_name": "Swivel Gun XR: Treasure Hunt", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Ahoy, me hearties! Dive into Swivel Gun XR: Treasure Hunt, the game where ye plunder riches right from your own home! \n\nUsing Roomscale Mixed Reality, transform your environment into 1 of 6 Fully destructible treasure hunting grounds. Each has their own traps and dangers, so be careful!\n\nWhere will ye hunt next?\n\nAVAST! FULL CONTENT RELEASE!\n> Made for Room Scale Mixed Reality <\n- 3 NEW Map Types to explore!\n- Limited Time COLLECTABLES\n- NEW Weapons & Enemies\n- NEW Traps and Dangers\n- Seasonal Hidden Map\n\nSo tell me, me hearties: where will ye hunt next?", "short_description": "Ahoy, me hearties! Dive into Swivel Gun XR: Treasure Hunt, the game where ye plunder riches right from your own home! \n\nUsing Roomscale Mixed Reality, transform your environment into 1 of 6 Fully destructible treasure hunting grounds. Each has their own traps and dangers, so be careful!\n\nWhere will ye hunt next?"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://pixelsofeight.wixsite.com/lander/sgth-privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Pixels of Eight LLC", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://pixelsofeight.wixsite.com/lander", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category"